WORK IN PROGRESS


## Run in Vagrant

    vagrant up
    vagrant provision

## Run in Docker

    sudo docker build -t ansible/django .

    sudo docker run -p 80 -p 443 \
      -v `pwd`:/srv/ansible/ \
      -v `pwd`/log/:/srv/site/log/ \
      -e DEBUG='True' \
      --rm -it ansible/django /srv/ansible/run.sh


## Role dependencies

- django
    - supervisor
    - sites
      - base
        - users
        - unattended
        - ntp

- postgis
    - postgres
      - base
        - users
        - unattended
        - ntp

- redis
    - base
      - users
        - unattended
        - ntp

- nginx
    - supervisor
    - base
      - users
      - unattended
      - ntp
